title: Jayun
description: Name in Korean 자연생활채식뷔페목포점, address 목포시 옥암동 1052 번지. Jayun is housed in a log-cabin style building. Offers a vegan buffet featuring Korean and some western food. Soups, salads, sandwiches, bread, rice, pasta, fruit, little veggie bundles artfully wrapped in leaves. Directions: There are no street signs, but a taxi driver will know the place if you have it written in Korean.
